# Tarball exclusions. `package.json:files` is the allowlist; this is the
# subtractive layer for paths that fall under an allowlisted directory but
# should not ship.
#
# Why we need .npmignore even with `files`: studio/docs is in the allowlist
# (architecture.md, cmo-api.md, FAQ.md and friends are useful); only the
# screenshots subdirectory bloats the tarball.

# 9.6 MB of dashboard PNGs that nothing in the install path reads.
studio/docs/screenshots/

# Local SQLite WAL/SHM that bun:sqlite leaves around when the studio is
# launched once at the marketing-cli root. Shouldn't ever ship.
marketing.db
marketing.db-wal
marketing.db-shm
studio/marketing.db
studio/marketing.db-wal
studio/marketing.db-shm

# Studio Next.js build/turbopack artifacts in case a dev forgot to clean.
studio/.next/
studio/.turbo/
studio/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
